===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|North America|Scotland|lang=en}} An [[underground railway]], especially for [[mass transit]] of people in [[urban]] areas.
# {{context|US|lang=en}} A rapid transit system, regardless of the elevation of its [[right of way]].
# {{context|British|lang=en}} underground walkway, [[tunnel]] for [[pedestrian]]s (called [[pedestrian underpass]] in US).

